{"comentario": {"textoComentario": "<p hash=\"382721192\" id=\"02272394Q-0d0ea264-9589eba42d79\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gabarito: <span style=\"color:#3498db\">Letra A</span></strong></p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<p hash=\"1434536383\" id=\"02272394Q-c05f4f5a-2c5ca7054890\" style=\"text-align:justify\">A quest&atilde;o pede para calcular qual o <strong>custo total do&nbsp;ferro</strong> utilizado para executar a viga detalhada na figura. Passemos aos c&aacute;lculos.</p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<p hash=\"2065425532\" id=\"02272394Q-50d0ca7e-a9270cc92eac\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Primeiramente precisamos verificar quais os di&acirc;metros utilizados e qual o <strong>total em metros</strong> de cada um deles.</p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<ul>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"406958002\" id=\"02272394Q-7c35e5cb-80e16e737d8e\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N1 - 3 barras de 16 mm com 7,60 m cada&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 22,80 m</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"623135229\" id=\"02272394Q-7e8a5184-1f0a34441882\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N2&nbsp;- 3 barras de 12.5&nbsp;mm com 7,20 m cada&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 21,60 m</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"783318902\" id=\"02272394Q-35bac9aa-1f6ee52d297d\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N3&nbsp;- 2&nbsp;barras de 5&nbsp;mm com 7,20 m cada&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 14,40 m</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1064059471\" id=\"02272394Q-cc1ec286-c5c88eaaaf27\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N4&nbsp;- 4&nbsp;barras de 10&nbsp;mm com 2,20 m cada&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 8,80 m</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"768565235\" id=\"02272394Q-09b613dc-9ee99009b056\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N5&nbsp;- 10&nbsp;barras de 6.3&nbsp;mm com 7,20 m cada&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 72,00&nbsp;m</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"611370436\" id=\"02272394Q-9b4eb412-cfe5511271c7\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N6&nbsp;- 36 barras de 6.3&nbsp;mm com 1,74&nbsp;m cada&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 62,64&nbsp;m</li>\u000d\u000a</ul>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<p hash=\"647688788\" id=\"02272394Q-4f357a03-806847f71039\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Agora que sabemos o total em metros, precisamos <strong>calcular em kg conforme a massa linear</strong> apresentada na tabela.</p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<ul>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1748434587\" id=\"02272394Q-6087bfd8-682fa378752c\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N1 - barras de 16 mm&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 36,48 kg</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1256192989\" id=\"02272394Q-0486f892-3c2b9b40ae45\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N2&nbsp;- barras de 12.5&nbsp;mm&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 21,60 kg</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"782056249\" id=\"02272394Q-0434d465-5be6cadfc59f\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N3&nbsp;- barras de 5&nbsp;mm&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 2,30 kg</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"514469093\" id=\"02272394Q-59f454e7-73283922970a\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N4&nbsp;- barras de 10&nbsp;mm&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 5,54 kg</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"606216499\" id=\"02272394Q-ab757edb-e5433127c7f4\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N5&nbsp;- barras de 6.3&nbsp;mm&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 18 kg</li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1821885397\" id=\"02272394Q-ab8bc194-c4b7bc90f54c\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N6&nbsp;- barras de 6.3&nbsp;mm&nbsp;&#x2192; Total = 15,66 kg</li>\u000d\u000a</ul>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<p hash=\"1707754183\" id=\"02272394Q-5f3138cc-f8f7d1ab5c59\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Finalmente, podemos <strong>calcular os pre&ccedil;os</strong> para chegar ao resultado final.</p>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<ul>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1725127935\" id=\"02272394Q-63163227-cd96d856e584\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N1&nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp;<span class=\"render-latex\" contenteditable=\"false\">36,48\\times9,50 = 346,56</span></li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1949530692\" id=\"02272394Q-e1c698e1-f8674fc2af95\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N2&nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp;<span class=\"render-latex\" contenteditable=\"false\">21,60\\times7,59 = 163,94</span></li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"943777793\" id=\"02272394Q-3e2401d4-85fc331166b1\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N3&nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp;<span class=\"render-latex\" contenteditable=\"false\">2,30\\times6,00 = 13,80</span></li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"609929472\" id=\"02272394Q-281376d4-c7fb3fae9878\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N4&nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp;<span class=\"render-latex\" contenteditable=\"false\">5,54\\times6,80 = 37,67</span></li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"1332772158\" id=\"02272394Q-0f8406b9-666262de1c41\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N5&nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp;<span class=\"render-latex\" contenteditable=\"false\">18,00\\times6,00 = 108,00</span></li>\u000d\u000a\u0009<li hash=\"86777404\" id=\"02272394Q-ed29beee-601665f74166\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">N6&nbsp;&#x2192;&nbsp;<span class=\"render-latex\" contenteditable=\"false\">15,66\\times6,00 = 93,96</span></li>\u000d\u000a</ul>\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a&nbsp;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a<p hash=\"1930340345\" id=\"02272394Q-49fcfb37-6753c72a72a3\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Somando estes valores, temos R$763,93. Como no enunciado pede que seja em <strong>n&uacute;mero inteiro</strong>, ent&atilde;o teremos <strong>R$764. Gabarito: <span style=\"color:#3498db\">Letra A</span></strong></p>","fotoProfessor": "https://cdn.tecconcursos.com.br/figuras/16416bef-4df6-420e-8f4e-d350575323f6","nomeProfessor": "Camila Rosa Vaz","urlProfessor": "camila","dataPublicacaoComentario": "28/04/2024","dataFormatadaParaHtml5": "2024-04-28"}}